y new entries in already-crowded soft commodity futures. If determined to express this view, the ONLY defensible structure is a defined-risk long call spread (not outright futures) with maximum loss capped at 1% of portfolio, entered after COT positioning normalizes below the 80th percentile — which is not today's setup.
